Password Strength Checker

Description
This Python-based Password Strength Checker helps users create robust and secure passwords by assessing their strength against essential criteria: length, uppercase and lowercase letters, numbers, and special characters. The tool offers real-time feedback and categorizes passwords as "Very Weak" to "Very Strong," ensuring better security for online accounts.  

Tech Stack 
- Programming Language: Python  
- Library: `re` (for regex-based pattern matching)  

Features 
- Evaluates password strength on five parameters.  
- Provides actionable feedback for improvement.  
- Lightweight, user-friendly, and ideal for educational or personal security projects.  

